request.description:
🚦 CALL THIS FIRST ON APP OPEN.

Returns whether the current driver has already started their day:
```json
// Shift already started:
{ "isStarted": true, "logId": "<ObjectId>", "role": "driver pickup" }

// Shift not started yet:
{ "isStarted": false }
```
- `isStarted: true`  → skip the meter photo screen, go directly to Dashboard.
- `isStarted: false` → show the Start Shift / Odometer screen (Step 2).
